                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Sleeper</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 21, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(In reply to Department’s cablegram of the 20th, Mr. Sleeper says the matter is
                    fully reported in dispatch 135, mailed this day, and that the alleged outrage is
                    not apparent.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
